      <h2 class="msa-page__heading">About MSA (Moon Style Apparel)</h2>
      <div class="msa-page__text rte">
        <p>Established in 2012, MSA Sourcing is a trusted buying and sourcing agency based in Pakistan, offering comprehensive solutions for international buyers seeking high-quality garments, textiles, apparel, and accessories. As a leading private-sector Textile Export Promotion House, we specialise in promoting and facilitating the global export of Pakistani textile products, especially in knitwear, denim and leather.</p>
        <p>With an integrated and total-solution approach, MSA Sourcing connects global buyers with reliable manufacturers, ensuring product quality, timely delivery, and smooth transactions. Our extensive network across Pakistan allows us to source a diverse range of textiles and apparel tailored to meet our clients' specific requirements.</p>
        <p>As experienced buying agents, our team ensures our clients receive premium products within competitive timelines and at the best market prices. We offer access to a wide selection of original and up-to-date designs, supported by efficient logistics and stringent quality control through our collaboration with other companies.</p>
        <p>At MSA Sourcing, our goal is to be your reliable partner in accessing the finest textile solutions Pakistan has to offer, efficiently, affordably, and with uncompromising quality.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
