    <div class="msa-page__block">
      <h3 class="msa-page__title">Charitable partner — MSA with SAVE DC</h3>
      <div class="msa-page__text rte">
        <p>At <strong>MSA</strong>, we believe that true business success is measured not just by profit but by leaving a positive impact on society. In partnership with <strong>Save the Deserving Children (SAVE DC)</strong>, we sponsor orphaned and underprivileged children across Pakistan, providing completely free education including school fees, textbooks, uniforms, and regular health checkups.</p>
        <p>This initiative supports the UN Sustainable Development Goals, particularly Quality Education (SDG 4) and Reduced Inequalities (SDG 10). Through SAVE DC's Sponsor a Child programme, companies and individuals can make a lasting difference.</p>
        <p><strong>MSA &amp; SAVE DC:</strong> Empowering tomorrow's leaders, today.</p>
